event.descr:

This trap is sent on initialization if the condition is detected. Subsequent traps occur only if there is a transition of the DCD signal from low to high. The affected serial port number is contained in pmTrapObjectSerialPortNumber. The affected serial port name is contained in pmTrapObjectSerialPortName.
